comments: He is not a crazy person, which already puts him in the top tenth percentile of all HCC teachers. I thought he was a very good teacher, but the tests annoyed me. We spent most classes learning how to do these spreadsheet-type things, but the tests were all these tricky true-false questions.
Very Knowledgeable, helpfull and kind. Always ready to help
Simply the best take his class

He is one of the best instructors. Repeats the subject if he feels the students are missing a point. The student that commented on Dec 19,10 should have failed the exam, even quoted a wrong course code . He never leaves the class on the contrary he closes the door during lectures to reduce noise, he give us reviews so exam questions are covered

It is true that this professor is easy. Yet, his class was extremely boring!!!! Professor loves to repeat same things over and over anain. He may be rude, I think. I saw how he looks at the students that bother him, or walk out the door during the class. His tests are pretty easy, but often you may get across the question that he did not talk about
Best Prof. uses new methods in teaching to make the class enjoyable. Always ask the students if they have questions. Recommend this class
super hot! easy A. i highly recommend this class.
He is the best prof ever!!! So nice, so helpful...easy A...the other person who commented badly on this prof obviously didnt do any work...i totally recommend to take this prof :)
Hes so awesome. I love this guy! Hes super helpful and answers all my questions. He is an easy A! TAKE THIS CLASS!!!!!!!!!!!! Hes so funny!!!!!!

This guy is rude, if you don\'t understand he just says the same thing in a louder voice. Don\'t ask too many questions, he\'ll start to ignore you. He also kinda calls you out in class if you make a mistake, sets you up when he knows it\'s a tricky question you won\'t catch. His tests are easy until the final, then those tricky questions take over.
